PSSI Jadi Trending Topic, Netizen Ramai Bahas Iwan Bule
02 Nov 2019, 15:01 by Adi Fida Rahman - detikInet


Foto: Rifkianto Nugroho/detikSport

Jakarta - Sepanjang Sabtu siang, timeline Twitter dihangatkan soal Kongres Luar Biasa (KLB) PSSI. Lebih-lebih saat Iwan Bule terpilih menjadi Ketua Umum PSSI yang baru.Lantaran ramai yang membicarakan, PSSI menjadi trending cukup lama di Twitter Indonesia. Lebih dari 15 ribu kicauan terkait organisasi yang menanungi persepakbolaan di Tanah Air itu.Berikut sejumlah kicauan netizen terkait PSSI dan ketua umumnya yang baru.



























Nah kalau kamu sendiri bagaimana pendapatnya bagaimana detikers? Simak Video "Menang Telak, Iwan Bule Ketua Umum PSSI 2019-2023"[Gambas:Video 20detik](afr/afr)
text:
PSSI Becomes Trending Topic, Netizens Crowded to Discuss Iwan Bule
02 Nov 2019, 15:01 by Adi Fida Rahman - detikInet


Photo: Rifkianto Nugroho / detikSport

Jakarta - Throughout Saturday afternoon, the Twitter timeline was warmed about the PSSI Extraordinary Congress (KLB). Even more so when Iwan Bule was elected as the new Chairperson of PSSI. Crowds talk about it, PSSI has been trending for a long time on Twitter Indonesia. More than 15 thousand tweets related to the organization that houses football in the country. Following a number of netizens related to PSSI and its new general chairman.



























Well, if you yourself, what do you think about detikers? Check out the video "Win a landslide victory, Iwan Bule Chairperson of PSSI 2019-2023" [Gambas: Video 20 seconds] (afr / afr)
